<item>
            <title>[MNG-479] unable to override the default central repository</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/MNG-479</link>
                <project id="12316922" key="MNG">Maven (Moved to GitHub Issues)</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Adding to my pom.xml:&lt;br/&gt;
....&lt;br/&gt;
    &amp;lt;repositories&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
        &amp;lt;repository&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
            &amp;lt;id&amp;gt;central&amp;lt;/id&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
            &amp;lt;name&amp;gt;custom repository&amp;lt;/name&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
            &amp;lt;url&amp;gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://maven.company.com/maven2&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://maven.company.com/maven2&lt;/a&gt;&amp;lt;/url&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
        &amp;lt;/repository&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
    &amp;lt;/repositories&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
....&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;did not override the central repository but instead uses the above configured repository as backup/mirror.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
